  "body": "I've just got my erigon node synced, soooo fast! But after playing with rpc calls got some questions:\r\n\r\nWhen I request {\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBlockByHash\",\"params\": [\"0x9a7c48f0e9779f731168e2ae319e404a2efd32dfa2d3ce0d3fb1466301f33be8\",true],\"id\":1}\r\nit returns 236 entries where one of them is -\r\n...,\r\n{\r\n\t\"blockHash\": \"0x9a7c48f0e9779f731168e2ae319e404a2efd32dfa2d3ce0d3fb1466301f33be8\",\r\n\t\"blockNumber\": \"0xc977b4\",\r\n\t\"from\": \"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\",\r\n\t\"gas\": \"0x5530a0\",\r\n\t\"gasPrice\": \"0xe2710488b\",\r\n\t\"maxPriorityFeePerGas\": \"0x59682f00\",\r\n\t\"maxFeePerGas\": \"0x159aea641f\",\r\n\t\"hash\": \"0xe8106c5e5df2313fc95e5bebfd1dfcadb8131f0e9c897f10be176f7e05ca2f96\",\r\n\t\"input\": \"<REMOVED TO MAKE IT SHORT>\",\r\n\t\"nonce\": \"0x1\",\r\n\t\"to\": null,\r\n\t\"transactionIndex\": \"0xd7\",\r\n\t\"value\": \"0x0\",\r\n\t\"type\": \"0x2\",\r\n\t\"chainId\": \"0x1\",\r\n\t\"v\": \"0x1\",\r\n\t\"r\": \"0x1c246ac65af899876ed70fcab16d9d96cfd6a7f02d1250217e4fac7038c1da26\",\r\n\t\"s\": \"0x25ad7d2adaf769e5e2bd99f3396ea7c7faa88cc143bcd6e1de7a7e5b9f826386\"\r\n},\r\n...\r\n\r\nplease note the field \"from\", which is 0x0.\r\n\r\nWhen I request this particular transaction via {\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionByHash\",\"params\": [\"0xe8106c5e5df2313fc95e5bebfd1dfcadb8131f0e9c897f10be176f7e05ca2f96\"],\"id\":1}\r\nI got the identical structure except it shows the correct \"from\" value which is \"0x71d6c3823bbbce39af789d2b063ad33b2ecda7d3\"\r\n\r\nIs it expected behavior or my DB got corrupted? I downloaded with \"2021.09.01-alpha\" and after full sync upgraded to \"2021.09.03-alpha\". Thanks!\r\n",
